    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the magic. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, showroom-ready condition and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away and pristine. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new but has that soul only a true enthusiast's car can offer, you\u2019ve found it. It's practically flawless and ready for its next adventure. Come by, have a coffee, and let's talk cars!",
