    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to acquire a truly surgical precision instrument. The naturally aspirated power plant features a revised intake plenum and optimized ECU mapping, delivering a perfectly linear torque curve that pulls relentlessly to the redline. The chassis rigidity is unparalleled, further enhanced by a custom-tuned suspension geometry that minimizes unsprung weight and maximizes mechanical grip through every apex. The limited-slip differential provides instantaneous lock-up, ensuring power delivery is as visceral as it is controlled. Every factory tolerance has been meticulously verified, and the finish exhibits a depth and clarity that rivals a fresh factory delivery. For the enthusiast who demands zero compromise in throttle response and lateral stability, this machine is beyond reproach.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
